OL,3,CReferee suspended after video emerges
OL,4,Cof him appearing to insult Jurgen Klopp
OL,6,FIt is not yet confirmed that the video
OL,7,Fis genuine, but it is understood PGMOL
OL,8,Fis treating it as genuine.
OL,10,FIn a statement it said: "David Coote
OL,11,Fhas been suspended with immediate
OL,12,Feffect pending a full investigation.
OL,13,FPGMOL will be making no further
OL,14,Fcomment until that process is
OL,15,Fcomplete."
OL,17,FIt is understood Liverpool are aware
OL,18,Fof the video but in light of an
OL,19,Finvestigation being launched do not
OL,20,Ffeel it would be appropriate to
OL,21,Fcomment.
