OL,3,CReferee suspended after video emerges
OL,4,Cof him appearing to insult Jurgen Klopp
OL,6,FKlopp was critical that Coote, as VAR,
OL,7,Fhad failed to award Liverpool a
OL,8,Fpenalty against Arsenal last season
OL,9,Fwhen Gunners midfielder Martin
OL,10,FOdegaard's hand made contact with the
OL,11,Fball.
OL,13,FCoote judged that Odegaard handled the
OL,14,Fball as he sought to keep his balance
OL,15,Fand did not advise on-field official
OL,16,FChris Kavanagh to review the incident.
OL,18,FKlopp said after the match: "I am
OL,19,Fpretty sure someone will come to
OL,20,Fexplain it to me why it was not a
OL,21,Fhandball but I don't know how?
